{"data":[{"date":"11:40 19/06","title":"B\u1ecb v\u1ee3 c\u1ea5m, ch\u00e0ng C\u0110V Mexico v\u1eabn \"l\u01b0\u1ee3n l\u1edd\" kh\u1eafp World Cup 2018 nh\u1edd h\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \"l\u1ea7y l\u1ed9i\"","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/bi-vo-cam-chang-cdv-mexico-van-luon-lo-khap-world-cup-2018-nho-hoi-ban-lay-loi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m fan Mexico n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap anh ch\u00e0ng C\u0110V t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c an \u1ee7i ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">World Cup l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, di\u1ec5n ra 4 n\u0103m m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n. M\u1ecdi C\u0110V \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e1t khao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed World Cup, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o VCK.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng anh ch\u00e0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u00ean Javier s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i Mexico l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc do v\u1ee3 c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Javier ph\u1ea5n ch\u1ea5n h\u01a1n, nh\u00f3m b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n g\u1ed3m 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd mua m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe bus c\u0169, g\u1eedi theo \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn B\u0110N. Nh\u1eadn xe t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, nh\u00f3m b\u1ea1n n\u00e0y l\u00e1i xuy\u00ean qua ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i Nga m\u00e0 Mexico thi \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean in h\u00ecnh Javier v\u1edbi k\u00edch c\u1ee1 si\u00eau l\u1edbn v\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh g\u1eedi v\u1ec1, gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 nh\u00f3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \"Javier\" xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1n bar t\u1ea1i Amsterdam, m\u1ed9t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c, u\u1ed1ng bia, l\u00e1i xe v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 h\u00f2a nh\u1ecbp v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1eafc h\u1eb3n \u1edf nh\u00e0, anh ch\u00e0ng Javier \"x\u1ecbn\" r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng \u0110T Mexico k\u00e9o d\u00e0i c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t, cho \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1eb9n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 SV\u0110 Luzhniki, n\u01a1i t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/photo-2-15293355895291528109243.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/photo-1-15293355895241897612728.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/photo-1-15293355870691569739307.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3704","checkdouble":"188915"},{"date":"10:42 19/06","title":"CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup cho \u0111\u1ea1i gia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea1i gia Italia v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1m t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga khan hi\u1ebfm nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i, Aleksandr Golovin n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u201cNh\u1eefng ch\u00fa g\u1ea5u\u201d \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng 5-0. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGolovin \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Nga t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CSKA Moscow. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n Nga</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n27 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho CSKA t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Nga, Golovin c\u00f3 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. \u1ede c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft, \u0111i b\u00f3ng cho t\u1edbi s\u00fat xa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n Golovin nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap Nga th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u vang d\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Juventus t\u1eeb suy ngh\u0129 mang anh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng. H\u1ecd g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi CSKA \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eaft x\u00edch m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" title=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/Juventus-muon-mua-Aleksandr-Golovin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng khi c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Golovin. M\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u00ean s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn CSKA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Juventus, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e2u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp nh\u01b0 Sami Khedira, Blaise Matuidi hay Stefano Sturaro, Bianconeri mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Miralem Pjanic trong kh\u00e2u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd tin c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Rodrigo Bentancur ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Aleksandr Golovin tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin-172-188557.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin-172-188557.html\">NHM Arsenal nh\u1eafn HLV Unai Emery: H\u00e3y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c mua Golovin</span><br>\r\n<span>Arsenal mua Aleksandr Golovin, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin-421-188547.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin-421-188547.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Nga 5-0 Saudi Arabia: \u0110i\u1ec3m 10 cho Aleksandr Golovin</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1eadn Nga vs Saudi Arabia b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3703","checkdouble":"188909"},{"date":"10:21 19/06","title":"Barca b\u1ecb sao Ajax n\u00f3i l\u1eddi cay \u0111\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/de-jong-khong-muon-toi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho Andres Iniesta trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c thay th\u1ebf Iniesta</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi Barcelona. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 34 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 x\u01b0a v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. Iniesta kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Vissel Kobe c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 v\u1edbi Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng bao g\u1ed3m t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Frenkie de Jong c\u1ee7a Ajax. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi tr\u00f4i qua ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin d\u00f9ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 CLB c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/De-Jong-khong-muon-toi-Barca-trong-tuong-lai-gan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca c\u1ea7n De Jong thay th\u1ebf Iniesta</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Jong c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 22 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n (6 t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb) v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 7 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng l\u1eabn d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 Lan khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ecb De Jong t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi t\u1edd Goal, De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Blaugrana h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n anh l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1eefu \u00edch cho hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Frenkie de Jong cua Ajax\" title=\"Frenkie de Jong cua Ajax\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/de-jong-khong-muon-toi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ecdc b\u00e1o T\u00e2y Ban Nha</em>\u201d, De Jong n\u00f3i. \u201c<em>\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea5p thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 ch\u00fa t\u00e2m v\u00e0o n\u00f3. T\u00f4i giao n\u00f3 cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft li\u1ec7u \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111ang suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y hay kh\u00f4ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i De Jong, Barca c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong \u0111\u00f3, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 Ilkay Gundogan c\u1ee7a Man City d\u00f9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-trao-doi-nguoi-voi-tottenham-180-188303.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/barca-muon-trao-doi-nguoi-voi-tottenham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-trao-doi-nguoi-voi-tottenham-180-188303.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi Tottenham</span><br>\r\n<span>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n c\u1ed9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rafinha \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Spurs nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ivan-rakitic-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-neymar-cap-ben-real-madrid-180-188263.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/ivan-rakitic-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-neymar-cap-ben-real-madrid.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ivan-rakitic-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-neymar-cap-ben-real-madrid-180-188263.html\">Ivan Rakitic n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Neymar c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid?</span><br>\r\n<span>Ivan Rakitic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Barca s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3702","checkdouble":"188908"},{"date":"09:56 19/06","title":"Man City ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/26/man-city-sap-co-jorginho-cua-napoli.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli. Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a Sky Sports, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Man City li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Jorginho l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1eeb l\u00e2u. \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang ch\u1edd 2 CLB \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thanh to\u00e1n, ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli gi\u00e1 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli gi\u00e1 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/26/man-city-sap-co-jorginho-cua-napoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli gi\u00e1 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh tr\u00ean Instagram v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Brazil. Anh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi Manchester ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf khi n\u00e0o 2 CLB th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Napoli m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng bao g\u1ed3m 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Man City t\u1ea1i Champions League h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 11.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Verona tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Napoli n\u0103m 2014. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Jorginho gi\u00fap l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Napoli th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Yaya Toure m\u1edbi ra \u0111i sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 Jorginho l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. Guardiola r\u1ea5t th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italia v\u00e0 tin anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/soc-raheem-sterling-tu-choi-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-man-city-172-188324.html\">S\u1ed1c: Raheem Sterling t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/doi-bong-dau-tien-dam-phan-voi-yaya-toure-172-188052.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Yaya Toure</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/neymar-tha-thinh-man-city-pep-van-rat-tinh-don-172-187954.html\">Neymar \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d Man City, Pep v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ec9nh \u0111\u00f2n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3701","checkdouble":"188904"},{"date":"10:42 19/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Fekir l\u1ea1i m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-fekir-lai-moi-goi-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nabil Fekir kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea5y m\u1ef1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-tuyen-phap-len-60-trieu-bang-172-187260.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Fekir</span> v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 6. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 v\u00e0 The Kop bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Fekir \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda Lyon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Fekir s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Fekir m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Fekir m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-fekir-lai-moi-goi-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Fekir m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Jean-Pierre Bernes m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea1i trao th\u00eam hy v\u1ecdng cho Liverpool trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Liverpool theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Fekir, Bernes cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cFekir kh\u00f4ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00ec\u2026 (Bernes \u1ea5p \u00fang), m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Lyon quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Fekir</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y, Lyon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Fekir \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cLyon mu\u1ed1n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Fekir \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 Lyon \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n n\u00e0y v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Fekir mong mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool nh\u01b0ng Lyon v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, khi m\u00e0 Lyon s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Champions League sau khi c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Nabil Fekir \u0111ang tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Australia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Fekir:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-cau-thu-ma-liverpool-co-the-mua-thay-vi-nabil-fekir-172-188319.html\">5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua thay v\u00ec Nabil Fekir</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lyon-chinh-thuc-xac-minh-thuc-hu-vu-liverpool-mua-fekir-172-188158.html\">Lyon ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c minh th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Fekir</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3700","checkdouble":"188906"},{"date":"11:03 19/06","title":"Arsenal s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 2 h\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/arsenal-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-bernd-leno.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, Arsenal \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Bernd Leno</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bernd Leno trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bernd Leno trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/arsenal-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-bernd-leno.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Bernd Leno</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leno \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 304 l\u1ea7n cho Bayer Leverkusen k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y n\u0103m 2011. Nh\u01b0ng theo tin \u0111\u1ed3n, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2018/19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Unai Emery \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Petr Cech ngay m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo. T\u1edd Bild kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y, Cech nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Th\u1ea7n g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi CH S\u00e9c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd chia tay s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-arsenal-chinh-thuc-don-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-emery-172-187828.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Stephan Lichtsteiner</span>. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Anh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi The Gunners.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis Papastathopoulos nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Emirates sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. Cha c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng Sokratis \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Manchester United \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201c\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Man United. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 7 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng\u201d, Charalambos Papastathopoulos chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t k\u00eanh radio c\u1ee7a Hy L\u1ea1p.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cMan United c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Dortmund. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Sokratis kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng con trai t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ecdn Arsenal\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/granit-xhaka-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-arsenal-172-188587.html\">Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chieu-mo-torreira-tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-172-188414.html\">Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Torreira: T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb h\u00f4m nay</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3699","checkdouble":"188910"},{"date":"07:31 19/06","title":"Sao H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/sao-ha-noi-doi-mat-an-treo-gio-sau-tran-thua-sai-gon-fc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF m\u1ed5 b\u0103ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Oseni hay trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a HAGL.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Dao-Duy-Khanh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh gi\u1eadt c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf v\u00e0o v\u00f9ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n v\u00e0o Nam \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. V\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y x\u1ea5u tr\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ea1ch 13 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t S\u00e0i G\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-5 chung cu\u1ed9c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u1ecb ng\u1eaft m\u1ea1ch 13 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 v\u00ec l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 75, trong l\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111ang d\u1eabn 4-2. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Duy Kh\u00e1nh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1eadt c\u00f9i ch\u1ecf v\u00e0o c\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Da Sylva trong l\u00fac ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i k\u00edn c\u1ee7a Duy Kh\u00e1nh d\u0129 nhi\u00ean qua m\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Thu\u1eadn&nbsp;song h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 98 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0110\u00e0o Duy Kh\u00e1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i t\u1eeb Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n g\u1eedi ki\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb l\u00ean ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1ed5 b\u0103ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, VFF l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t nghi\u00eam v\u1edbi c\u00e1c l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i treo gi\u00f2 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Douglas Tardin, trong khi Oseni c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hai tr\u1eadn c\u0169ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u1ea1m M\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a&nbsp;SLNA.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung-168-188784.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung-168-188784.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n nhung?</span><br>\r\nTrong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a n\u1eb7ng h\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t chi\u1ec1u qua, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho-291-188777.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho-291-188777.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf xin - cho?</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf xin - cho v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i \u1edf V-League, b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nghi v\u1ea5n quanh tr\u1eadn thua...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/sai-gon-vs-ha-noi-vong-14-vleague-2018-372-188725.html\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): Da Sylva l\u1eadp poker, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0110\u00f4 thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</span><br>\r\nB\u1ed1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Da Sylva \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC gi\u00e0nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Thua tr\u1eadn, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf con s\u1ed1 13.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-family: Antenna-Regular, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3698","checkdouble":"188892"},{"date":"18:07 18/06","title":"Qu\u00e2n b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/quan-bau-duc-du-giai-u17-quoc-gia-2018-voi-thanh-tich-vo-cung-an-tuong.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb, HAGL kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 VCK U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>U17 HAGL l\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U17 HAGL l\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U17 HAGL l\u1ea1i d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/U17-HAGL.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U17 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u 17/6 v\u1eeba qua, l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh, trong \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i U17 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 6-3 chung cu\u1ed9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 bao g\u1ed3m: U17 C\u00f4ng An Nh\u00e2n D\u00e2n, Viettel (B\u1ea3ng A); SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, S\u00f4ng Lam Ngh\u1ec7 An (B\u1ea3ng B); HAGL, Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (B\u1ea3ng C); An Giang (B\u1ea3ng D) v\u00e0 U17 PVF (\u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng cai VCK).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ebb nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. U17 HAGL l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 26 \u0111i\u1ec3m. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 8/10 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, ho\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o n\u00e0o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi 37 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ebb Gia Lai c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u1edbi +29 b\u00e0n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U17 Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 26/06 \u0111\u1ebfn 06/07/2018 t\u1ea1i Trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb PVF t\u1ea1i V\u0103n Giang, H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ec5 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m x\u1ebfp l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 20/6 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL: Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong-168-188827.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong-168-188827.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 HAGL, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m th\u01b0 tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i sau chu\u1ed7i 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai t\u1ea1i V-League...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hagl-thua-nhan-diem-yeu-sau-tran-thua-shb-da-nang-168-188740.html\">HLV HAGL th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu sau tr\u1eadn thua SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018-325-188738.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-da-nang-21-hagl-vong-14-vleague-2018-325-188738.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL (V\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. \u0110\u1ed7 Merlo san b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00f2n H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3697","checkdouble":"188836"},{"date":"21:58 18/06","title":"Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Th\u00e1i Lan l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/18/viet-nam-thai-lan-len-ke-hoach-dang-cai-world-cup-2034.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u0103ng cai VCK World Cup 2034 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra sau \u0111\u00e2y 16 n\u0103m n\u1eefa.</h2><h2>Th\u00e1i Lan, Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, li\u00ean minh M\u1ef9 - Canada \u2013 Mexico \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2026. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 World Cup m\u00e0 FIFA s\u1ebd \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 l\u00ean 48 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f9ng Th\u00e1i Lan, Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f9ng Th\u00e1i Lan, Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/5902-world_cup_eyvd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2034 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1. V\u00e0 theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb t\u1edd The Straits Times, ba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00f4ng Nam A\u0301 g\u1ed3m Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Indonesia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 se\u0303 gia\u0300nh quy\u00ea\u0300n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u1ee6y ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh FIFA, Tengku Abdullah Sultan Ahmad Shah ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o Li\u00ean minh ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m 2034.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i (\u0110\u00f4ng Nam A\u0301) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00ea\u0309 hi\u00ea\u0323n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00ec co\u0301 ba \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ed1n qu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f4\u0300ng h\u01a1\u0323p ta\u0301c nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec M\u1ef9, Mexico v\u00e0 Canada \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 n\u0103m 2026.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia trong khu v\u01b0\u0323c n\u00e0y co\u0301 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0323c c\u01a1 h\u00f4\u0323i. V\u00ea\u0300 khi\u0301a ca\u0323nh na\u0300y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u01a1 s\u1edf h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00f4ng Nam A\u0301 s\u1ebd b\u0103\u0301t ki\u0323p v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3. T\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n 16 n\u0103m n\u1eefa v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin b\u1ea5y nhi\u00eau c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7\u201d, \u00f4ng Ahmad Shah cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai, c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 nh\u01b0 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ra tranh t\u00e0i \u1edf s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ngo\u00e0i li\u00ean minh Vi\u1ec7t \u2013 Th\u00e1i \u2013 Indonesia, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u0103ng cai k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m 2014. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034 s\u1ebd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2026.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-viet-nam-co-3-quan-xanh-truoc-them-aff-cup-2018-168-185506.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/dt-viet-nam-co-3-quan-xanh-truoc-them-aff-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-viet-nam-co-3-quan-xanh-truoc-them-aff-cup-2018-168-185506.html\">\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 3 qu\u00e2n xanh tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m AFF Cup 2018</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch AFF Cup 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd t\u00ecm 3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i thi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-2-dieu-kien-de-dt-viet-nam-du-world-cup-465-188358.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-2-dieu-kien-de-dt-viet-nam-du-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-2-dieu-kien-de-dt-viet-nam-du-world-cup-465-188358.html\">HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung ch\u1ec9 ra 2 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 World Cup</span><br>\r\nHLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 World Cup, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n hai v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-riedl-noi-phu-ve-giac-mo-world-cup-cua-bong-da-viet-168-188640.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-riedl-noi-phu-ve-giac-mo-world-cup-cua-bong-da-viet.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-riedl-noi-phu-ve-giac-mo-world-cup-cua-bong-da-viet-168-188640.html\">HLV Riedl n\u00f3i ph\u0169 v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t</span><br>\r\nB\u00ean l\u1ec1 VCK World Cup 2018, c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00f4ng Alfred Riedl \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3696","checkdouble":"188859"},{"date":"19:22 18/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 18/6: Chi 170 tri\u1ec7u euro, MU n\u1ed5 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/13/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-186-chi-170-trieu-euro-mu-no-bo-doi-bom-tan-vao-dau-thang-7.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18/6.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi 170 tri\u1ec7u euro, MU n\u1ed5 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 186 MU chi 170 tri\u1ec7u euro mua 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 186 MU chi 170 tri\u1ec7u euro mua 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Gareth Bale</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDaily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh MU ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Joshua Kimmich n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Joshua Kimmich ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Abendzeitung \u0111\u01b0a tin, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Anh s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u00ec... thi\u1ebfu tham v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sam Allardyce ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng cao \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Anh ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-se-thanh-cong-o-world-cup-2018-vi-thieu-tham-vong-421-188839.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/dt-anh-se-thanh-cong-o-world-cup-2018-vi-thieu-tham-vong.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-se-thanh-cong-o-world-cup-2018-vi-thieu-tham-vong-421-188839.html\">\u0110T Anh s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u00ec... thi\u1ebfu tham v\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\nSam Allardyce ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng cao \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Anh ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Alisson s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/Real-Madrid-mua-Alisson-thanh-cong-voi-gia-52-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alisson s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid s\u1eafp \u0111\u00f3n Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 70 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Man City chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Toni Kroos</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Pep nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Wenger ca ng\u1ee3i t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kante, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ca ng\u1ee3i t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 sao Porto v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Porto chi ban Alex Telles voi gia 35 trieu bang\" title=\"Porto ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Alex Telles v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/liverpool-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-porto-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alex Telles</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo A Bola, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Alex Telles c\u1ee7a Porto v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-porto-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-172-188798.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/liverpool-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-porto-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-porto-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-172-188798.html\">Liverpool s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao Porto v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nLiverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Telles c\u1ee7a Porto \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, The Kop ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>De Bruyne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thomas Meunier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kevin De Bruyne, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real chi 150 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ed9ng Navas mua Salah</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diario Gol cho r\u1eb1ng Real \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Salah, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 150 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ed9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Keylor Navas \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu Salah.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3695","checkdouble":"188844"},{"date":"04:55 19/06","title":"Hazard: \"Chelsea ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1eadm m\u1edbi gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/hazard-chelsea-phai-chi-dam-moi-giu-duoc-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea sau m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, ngay t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m anh chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nHazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Eden Hazard c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i \u1edf l\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f2n t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 t\u1ea1i London, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. Nh\u1edd Chelsea, t\u00f4i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1eadt d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra \u0111i, sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho CLB. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i \u0111ang ch\u1edd xem li\u1ec7u HLV Conte c\u00f3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay ra \u0111i&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i CLB trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup\" title=\"Hazard vs Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/hazard-chelsea-phai-chi-dam-moi-giu-duoc-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i CLB trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ng\u00e0y mai, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i n\u1eefa, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ng\u1eebng nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u00f4i, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec. \u1ede l\u1ea1i hay ra \u0111i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Chelsea.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu CLB c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0i h\u01a1i, m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n l\u1edbn, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa&rdquo; &ndash; Eden Hazard chia s\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00cdt gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama, trong \u0111\u00f3 Hazard g\u00f3p m\u1ed9t pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1ea3i qua th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0110T n\u00e0o c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;HLV \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh trong hi\u1ec7p 2, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn n\u1eefa. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi&rdquo; &ndash; Eden Hazard k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Bi 3-0 Panama\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Thong-so-Bi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188867.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188867.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 c\u00f3 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khai th\u00f4ng ngay sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 v\u1edbi si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Mertens v\u00e0 c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf gi\u00e0nh th\u1ebf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-bi-30-panama-421-188866.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/Thong-ke-Bi-vs-Panama---Bang-G-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-bi-30-panama-421-188866.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n B\u1ec9 vs Panama 3-0, b\u1ea3ng G World...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3694","checkdouble":"188884"},{"date":"17:49 18/06","title":"K\u00e9m mi\u1ebfng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/2/8/kem-mieng-u23-viet-nam-bong-da-thai-lan-gap-rut-chuan-bi-cho-asiad.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong th\u1eddi gian qua, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i y\u00ean. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u00e9m mi\u1ebfng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASI h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u00e9m mi\u1ebfng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASI h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/8/u23-thai-lan-that-bai-ldbd-thai-quyet-tam-cai-cach.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi c\u00e1c \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Malaysia t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t khu v\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 U23 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tay tr\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n b\u1eb1ng tham v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i v\u1ed1n d\u00e0nh cho l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23+3 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan (FAT) \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 MFF Invitation Cup 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Myanmar.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i MFF Invitation Cup 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y m\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 5/8, quy t\u1ee5 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng bao g\u1ed3m ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U23 Myanmar v\u00e0 c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi U23 Th\u00e1i Lan, U23 Bahrain, ri\u00eang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ed9i U19 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Myanmar c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 U23 Th\u00e1i Lan th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD 17 t\u1ea1i Incheon H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u0103m 2014, \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u0169ng '\u00f4ng k\u1eb9' c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 nh\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c hay Jordan \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 Ch\u00f9a v\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-dich-danh-3-cau-thu-co-the-lo-hen-voi-asiad-2018-168-187949.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-dich-danh-3-cau-thu-co-the-lo-hen-voi-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-dich-danh-3-cau-thu-co-the-lo-hen-voi-asiad-2018-168-187949.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00edch danh 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, HLV Park Hang Seo cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00ean h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-188634.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-tre-binh-duong-bat-ngo-vi-duoc-lot-vao-danh-sach-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-188634.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Thanh Th\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3693","checkdouble":"188833"},{"date":"14:58 18/06","title":"Fan n\u1eef s\u1ed1 1 Peru l\u00e0m lo\u1ea1n kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i t\u1ea1i Nga","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/fan-nu-so-1-peru-lam-loan-khan-dai-tai-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nissu Cauti t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 fan n\u1eef n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0110T Peru m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i. \u1ede World Cup 2018, Nissu c\u0169ng sang Nga \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">&quot;Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u&quot; fan n\u1eef n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng c\u1ee7a Nissu Cauti \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb 3 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Peru chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i Copa America 2015 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Chile. Nissu v\u1edbi bi\u1ec7t danh &quot;em g\u00e1i&quot; Peru lu\u00f4n khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c m\u00e1y quay ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u00f4 khi di\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1ch \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n khoe tr\u1ecdn v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p 3 v\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m, Nissu c\u00f2n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ebfu Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Peru trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Montevideo. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, Edinson Cavani \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap Uruguay gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Nissu \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a tr\u00fat b\u1ecf xi\u00eam y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1nh m\u00e0y r\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t phen m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u00f9ng \u0110T Peru, Nissu \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 36 n\u0103m qua &quot;La Rojiblanca&quot; m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tham d\u1ef1. R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc cho Peru v\u00e0 &quot;em g\u00e1i&quot; Nissu, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u00e2m c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ee7a Nissu - &quot;Bravo, Peru. Bra off, Nissu&quot; (Peru ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean, qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o Nissu tr\u00fat xu\u1ed1ng), ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t Peru ch\u01a1i kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/nissu2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3692","checkdouble":"188819"}]}